	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你還問我在做什麼，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當然是在製作
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />啊！
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種事就是要趁著興頭上，<delay frames="40" />
想做的時候<delay8 />
一鼓作氣做才讚啊！
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />心無旁鶩做著ＤＩＹ的時候啊，<delay20 />
總覺得跟騎在機車上奔馳<delay8 />
有點像哩！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay20 />你要不要也做做看？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就可以教你哩！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那就麻煩你了～！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不用了沒關係</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay20 />那我就<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再稍微<delay8 />加工一下囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯？<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" />，
難道你也知道<delay20 />怎麼製作
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我知道喔！</message>
	<message label="008_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">算是吧！</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來是這樣啊，<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="3" />，真有你的，<delay20 />
挺厲害的嘛！</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說是這麼說，<delay20 />
<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是你現在<delay8 />包包都滿了啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚點<delay8 />再來找我吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿嘿，<delay20 />我就覺得會有這種狀況，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以提前<delay8 />把方程式準備好了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來，<delay8 />不用客氣，收下吧！</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自己動手做其實還滿有趣的喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="1" />感覺手就很巧，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說不定能做得比我還好哩！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay20 />的方程式<delay8 />
我姑且還是交給你啦。<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你有死黨想要，<delay8 />就替我轉送吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟<delay8 />我已經知道這東西該怎麼做了，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<delay8 />有其他人想做這個，<delay20 />
我也想讓大家都能知道，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果大家都開始<delay20 />用ＤＩＹ<delay8 />
製作<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說不定會成為一股小小的熱潮喔。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在這邊<delay20 />準備好了<delay8 />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />的方程式，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在就給你吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果打算製作這個，<delay20 />
首先得先準備好南瓜喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />機會難得，<delay20 />你也要來
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />試著種植南瓜嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">如果你想要<delay8 />改造這個的話，<delay8 />
就必須先準備好
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對應顏色的南瓜喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要大量種植，
總有一天能種出不同顏色的南瓜。<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就當成是經營家庭菜園，好好加油吧。</message>
	<message label="032" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />你是來拿<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛才沒能交給你的東西，對吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼你就收下這個吧！</message>
	<message label="033" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉唷，<delay20 />你已經知道<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個方程式了啊。</message>
	<message label="034" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那正好，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我手上剛好<delay20 />多出很多<colour id="1" />南瓜<colour id="65535" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就<delay8 />收下吧。</message>
	<message label="035" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果那個<colour id="1" />南瓜<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
能為你派上用場就好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="036" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣你就不需要相同的東西了吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過你都難得來一趟了，<delay8 />
我也不好意思讓你空手而回<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay20 />那我就給你那個好了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然不是什麼貴重的東西，<delay8 />
請收下這個<colour id="1" />糖果<colour id="65535" />吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />萬聖節也快到了，<delay20 />
你就好好保管到那時候吧。</message>
	<message label="037" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">在送你<colour id="1" />糖果<colour id="65535" />後，<delay20 />我也突然<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開始期待起萬聖節了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
